  "duaMeaning1": "ɔda wan dɛn de pre se, ‘Wi Masta, gi wi gud na dis wɔl ɛn na di layf we de afta, ɛn protɛkt wi frɔm di sɔfa we di Faya de mek wi sɔfa.’",
  "duaMeaning2": "Gɔd nɔ de lod ɛni sol wit mɔ pas wetin i ebul fɔ bia: ɛni wan de gɛt ɛni gud we i dɔn du, ɛn sɔfa in bad- ‘ Masta, nɔ tek wi fɔ wok if wi fɔgɛt ɔ mek mistek. Masta, nɔ lod wi lɛk aw Yu bin lod di wan dɛn we bin de bifo wi. Masta, nɔ lod wi pas wetin wi gɛt trɛnk fɔ bia. Fɔgiv wi, fɔgiv wi, ɛn sɔri fɔ wi. Yu na wi Protɛkta, so ɛp wi agens di wan dɛn we nɔ biliv.’",
  "duaMeaning3": "‘Wi Masta, nɔ mek wi at kɔmɔt biɛn afta Yu dɔn gayd wi. Gi wi Yu sɔri-at: Yu na di wan we de gi ɔltɛm.",
  "duaMeaning4": "Masta, mek mi ɛn mi pikin dɛn kɔntinyu fɔ pre. Wi Masta, aksept mi ​​rikwest.",
  "duaMeaning5": "ɛn put yu wing dɔŋ wit ɔmbul to dɛn wit gudnɛs ɛn se, ‘Masta, sɔri fɔ dɛn, jɔs lɛk aw dɛn bin de kia fɔ mi we a bin smɔl.’",
  "duaMeaning6": "Gɔd fɔ ɔp, di wan we rili de kɔntrol. [Prɔfɛt], nɔ rɔsh fɔ rid bifo di rivyu dɔn ful-ɔp bɔt se, ‘Masta, mek a no mɔ!’",
  "duaMeaning7": "Se [Prɔfɛt], ‘Masta, fɔgiv ɛn sɔri: Yu gɛt sɔri-at pas ɔlman.’",
  "duaMeaning8": "di wan dɛn we de pre se, ‘Wi Masta, gi wi gladi at pan wi man ɔ wɛf ɛn pikin dɛn. Mek wi gud ɛgzampul to di wan dɛn we no Yu’.",
